f. Control over subsidiaries

Note 11 describes that Kunshan Chimei Materials Technology Corp. (“KSCMMT”) is a subsidiary of the Corporation although the Corporation only holds less than half of the voting power of KSCMMT. After considering the Corporation’s absolute size of holding in KSCMMT and the contractual arrangements between the Corporation and other investors, potential voting interests and other factors, management concluded that the Corporation has a sufficiently dominant voting interest to direct the relevant activities of KSCMMT, and therefore, the Corporation has control over KSCMMT.
